episode: I apprehensive about my home made cake.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I apprehensive about my home made cake result

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: What's making you nervous about it?

dialogue.speaker: Human

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That can be a big mistake, are you worried it won't rise?

dialogue.message: Yes I worried a lot

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I can imagine, that's frustrating, especially if it's for a special occasion.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Aww, I'm sure they'll still love it, kids are usually forgiving.

dialogue.message: Absolutely they really meant my effort and didn't noticed any mistake

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's sweet, they appreciate the thought and love behind it.

dialogue.message: Yeah its true

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's the thought that counts, not the perfection.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yes, next time I will make more better one for them

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: I'm sure they're looking forward to it already.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Of course I go to made another choco cake

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Chocolate cake is always a winner with kids!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yes I don't want to disappoint them, so I decide to make their favorite

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's so thoughtful of you, I'm sure they'll be thrilled.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
